.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, punk, ambient, folk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, surfing, snowboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
4. the fan of punk is the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of trance and the fan of punk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk     | ambient           | trance | folk  |
| Sport         | soccer | volleyball | surfing   | snowboarding |

