.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, metal, funk
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, scooter, skateboard
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the fan of dubstep is between the person driving the bike and the fan of metal##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | hip-hop | dubstep | metal      |
| Transport     | scooter | bike    | ship  | skateboard |

