.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, rowing, cricket
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, jet-ski, van, bus
1. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person driving the van##2
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | volleyball | cricket | rowing     | water-polo   |
| Transport   | van   | jet-ski     | bus | subway |

