2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the coach##1
3. the architect is on the right of the coach##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the coach is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | paramedic | security-guard | coach | architect |
| Transport   | roller         | taxi       | bus    | trike         |

