.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, banana, eggplant, papaya
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing, weightlifting, golf
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating banana##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person eating banana and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | papaya   | eggplant      | banana   | pomegranate  |
| Sport   | golf | surfing | weightlifting | snowboarding |

