.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, apricot, radish, watermelon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, zombie, crime, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person eating apricot is between the person eating watermelon and the person eating banana##2
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | banana     | apricot | watermelon   | radish        |
| Movie-Genre   | western | crime   | zombie | comedy |

