.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, woodworking, collecting, photography
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, jazz, r&b, electronic
1. the fan of r&b is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of jazz##1
5. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the fan of jazz is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | collecting | photography | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | r&b          | jazz     | electronic  | country     |

