2. the accountant is between the person watching drama movies and the social-worker##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
4. the social-worker is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | social-worker | accountant | chef | pilot     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | thriller    | drama   | scientific |

