.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, british, egyptian, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, car, helicopter, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the brazilian is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the egyptian is between the person driving the helicopter and the british##2
4. the brazilian is on the right of the egyptian##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | turkish | british | egyptian | brazilian |
| Transport     | ship     | car   | quad-bike | helicopter  |

