.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, dutch, indonesian
4 different pets are kept: snake, frog, cat, fish
1. the american is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the indonesian is the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the snake and the japanese##2
4. the owner of the fish is the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | american | dutch |
| Pet           | cat  | fish  | frog | snake      |

