2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the colombian is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is between the nigerian and the japanese##2
5. the japanese is the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | colombian   | nigerian   | indian | japanese |
| Sport         | skateboarding | tennis | cricket     | handball    |

