.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, video-games, magic-tricks, camping
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, ferret, hedgehog
1. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is between the owner of the lizard and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks    | camping     | baking | video-games |
| Pet     | rat | hedgehog | ferret       | lizard     |

 